  "format": "A live New York City movie draft at the 92nd Street Y. Sean, Amanda, and Chris Ryan are joined by Blank Check's Griffin Newman and David Sims, each filling a six-slot roster across Drama, Comedy, Action / Horror / Thriller, Oscar Winner, Blockbuster, and Subway. The room votes; David Sims wins.",
  "segments": [
